## Monorepo Structure
```
intellect/
├── packages/
│   ├── api/          ← FastAPI — HTTP layer, routes, auth
│   ├── agents/       ← LangGraph agent system
│   │   ├── query_router/
│   │   ├── privacy_guard/
│   │   ├── pricing/
│   │   └── intelligence/
│   ├── web/          ← React dashboard
│   └── shared/       ← Pydantic models, types, constants
├── openspec/specs/
├── .cursor/rules/
├── docker-compose.yml
├── PRD.md
├── ARCHITECTURE.md
└── TASKS.md
```

